{"tid":2094173,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[神作噬謊者作者迫稔雄出品］巴突克戰舞討論區2","createTime":"2020-07-04T11:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T04:48:38.000Z","uid":96182,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6f56d4cfbb94de37a555ba6b938b5983fe6bbdca","tid":2094173,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T11:49:24.000Z","msg":"舊post沉左，反正新刊再開開個新post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zGgcOoGW7yM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzGgcOoGW7yM&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=40c5836d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zGgcOoGW7yM</a><br />\n<br />\n劇情簡介<br />\n在極其普通的家庭長大的，總有着未知的孤獨感與束縛感的女子高中生三條一里。<br />\n在便利店被強盜襲擊的那個瞬間,體驗了非常不可思議的身體本能&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n這就是，與她有關的名為解放的故事，拉開了帷幕。<br />\n<br />\n音樂、格鬥、舞蹈、宗教...融合人類百學的戰舞&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">卡波耶拉</span>&rdquo;。<br />\n&ldquo;漫畫力的追求者&rdquo;迫稔雄全力以赴，創作的異類青春大河劇，開幕！<br />\n<br />\n有睇個噬謊者既巴打就會知呢個作者出品一定係正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然今套冇噬謊果種痴線鬥智，不過打鬥場面方面有過之而無不及<br />\n不同於噬謊者既超人式戰鬥，巴突克既動作場面更講求現實<br />\n但唔代表d動作場面會唔華麗<br />\n而且更重要係因為作者本人都真係有學卡波耶拉，所以係畫得勁流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yeUw8RC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyeUw8RC.gif&h=98da1486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/javXjYp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjavXjYp.gif&h=0c8d8988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節錄自作者twitter<br />\n<br />\n不過某程度上呢部作品有個缺點都係同噬謊者一樣<br />\n就係要等到佢入戲肉開始先會真正好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一黎作者需要時間鋪排故事<br />\n好老實講頭果十零話真係會有d唔知主線係咩既感覺<br />\n不過一揭開某個角色既秘密開始個故事就會一氣呵成咁落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二黎作者畫細路既畫功係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過放心，一入戲肉主角群就會大個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變到又靚又型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜本作品叫好不叫座，單行本銷量麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由岩岩最新85話起轉左去web版連載，應該係雙週星期六先更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送上小小場面引大家入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ls3io5H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLs3io5H.png&h=b24d8521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UU3Mc25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUU3Mc25.png&h=167f2776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wAuCSew.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwAuCSew.jpg&h=ab060d50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31c73137f8edcbaa796df9281351f2f5f02e8551","tid":2094173,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYSeMGb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYSeMGb.jpg&h=ac542b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npush<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd21fe6109cc2d37b48ed6da7bb1e4639f0edf4","tid":2094173,"uid":96182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":